definition: dew point/(coll.) (of a woman) to expose one of the three areas (nipples and genitals)
dew/syrup/nectar/outdoors (not under cover)/to show/to reveal/to betray/to expose

point/dot/drop/speck/o'clock/point (in space or time)/to draw a dot/to check on a list/to choose/to order (food in a restaurant)/to touch briefly/to hint/to light/to ignite/to pour a liquid drop by drop/(old) one fifth of a two-hour watch 更[geng1]/dot stroke in Chinese characters/classifier for items

sentences.english: Showing the arm a little bit is going to make you look taller and leaner.
sentences.chinese: 露點胳膊出來將使你看起來苗條修長。

sentences.english: Lowers compressed air dewpoints for better equipment efficiency.
sentences.chinese: 降低壓縮空氣露點，使設備的效率更高。

sentences.english: I weep–the dew twinkles white on the green mosses.
sentences.chinese: 相思黃葉落，白露點青苔。

sentences.english: The operation condition of the dryer to any pressure points, not with the control flow.
sentences.chinese: 乾燥器的工況決定了壓力凝露點，而非用其調節流量。

sentences.english: You can reveal a point for me, where is that fairy hole ?
sentences.chinese: 能不能給我透露點啊，那個仙人洞是個什麼地方？

sentences.english: Hey guys, I just want to share some small information about the upcoming patch.
sentences.chinese: 我想在這裏給大家透露點下個版本的一些小信息。

sentences.english: Desalination by dewvaporation process is a novel brackish and seawater desalination method.
sentences.chinese: 露點蒸發淡化技術是一種新的苦鹹水和海水淡化方法。

sentences.english: Surface temperature is 3℃ less than Dew-point.
sentences.chinese: 表面溫度低於露點溫度3℃。

sentences.english: Cooling after the air pressure dew point is the minimum to 2 degrees.
sentences.chinese: 經降溫後的空氣壓力露點最低可達2℃。

sentences.english: Apply west Japan technology in dehumidifying wheel, dew Points are stable.
sentences.chinese: 採用日本西部技研除溼輪，露點穩定。

sentences.english: The practice proves that the dewpoint transmitter is an effective measuring means in the measurement of the humidity of pressurized air.
sentences.chinese: 實踐證明露點儀是檢測壓縮空氣溼度的有效計量手段。

sentences.english: Polymerization of any unconverted styrene and diolefins is accelerated at the dew point condition.
sentences.chinese: 在露點條件下苯乙烯和二烯烴的聚合反應會加速進行。

sentences.english: Describes the general configuration and work principle of the dew point indirect evaporative cooler.
sentences.chinese: 描述露點間接蒸發冷卻器的一般結構和工作原理。

sentences.english: It also adopts double condenser structure to ensure the lower return air temperature and dew point .
sentences.chinese: 採用雙冷凝器結構，確保更低的迴風溫度及露點。

sentences.english: This temperature adjustment is necessary to ensure that the dewpoint is not reached.
sentences.chinese: 爲了確保不達到露點，溫度調整是必要的。

sentences.english: When the pressure of condensate gas falls to dew point below, its phase will change.
sentences.chinese: 壓力降低到露點以下時凝析氣會發生相態變化。
